snippet.title: Hello Neighbor Pre-Launch Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
3 days to go! Pre-Order now on Steam - http://store.steampowered.com/app/521890

Hello Neighbor is a Stealth Horror game about sneaking into your creepy neighbor's house. Coming to Xbox One & PC this Friday, December 8th! Join us:

Discord - https://discord.gg/hyQcyev
Facebook  - https://www.facebook.com/tinyBuildGames/
Twitter - http://twitter.com/tinyBuild
Official website: http://HelloNeighborGAME.com
